    "body": "thanks for looking into this\r\n\r\nI believe it is this line\r\nhttps://github.com/gakonst/foundry/blob/f48e76ed4e1406ac25ac8eec0e87feab505e6f2f/cli/src/forge.rs#L57\r\n\r\nthere is some funny business going on with canonicalize on windows that's why the `dunce` crate exists\r\nhttps://crates.io/crates/dunce\r\n\r\nso if you'd like to submit a fix then we need\r\n* `cargo add dunce` in the `cli` folder\r\n* replace `let root = std::fs::canonicalize(root)?;` with `let root = dunce::canonicalize(root)?;`\r\n\r\nwhile you're at it you could check for more usages of `std::fs::canonicalize` cc #378 \r\n\r\n ",
